                    <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 mr-2 animate-pulse"></span>
                    v1.0 is now live
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-5xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl animate-fade-in-up">
                    <span class="block">We Collect Your</span>
                    <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600">Shit Bug 💩</span>
