                <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 animate-fade-in-up delay-100 leading-relaxed">
                    Transform chaos into clarity. Monitor, analyze, and resolve production errors instantly with AI-powered insights. Ship with confidence, fix bugs 10x faster, and reclaim your peace of mind.
                </p>
